<p>CNN：Europe tried a scalpel on the second wave. Now it's going back to the sledgehammer</p>
<p>Vox：European countries with spiraling Covid-19 outbreaks are shutting back down</p>
<p>BBC：Coronavirus: Macron declares second national lockdown in France</p>
<p>Reaction：Germany’s second wave shows why it is no coronavirus utopia</p>
<p>Spiegel：“We Are Threatened By a Second Wave If We Don’t Act Very Quickly”</p>
